Apantisi paratiroume oti to ACF 1 exei autoxorlation 0.99. Pragma pou simenei oti exoume sxedon tautisi (kati to opoio itan anamenomeno afou 1 imera den epireazei simantika tin xronosira pou exei parokipsei apo paratirisis 2 xronon).

print(acf(x, lag.max = 2, plot = FALSE))

X. ( cal AC(y,k) k 

AC <- function(y,k) {
  myACF <- acf(x, lag.max = k, plot = FALSE)
  return(unlist(myACF$acf)[k+1])
}

test <- AC(x,2)
test

R(1) MA(1)

Paratirisis 1) Paratiroume oti to monrelo ARIMA(1,0,0) den kanei poli kalo fit dioti exei statistika simantika residuals kai kai mi statistika simantika p-values 2) Omoios paratirite kai gia to ARIMA(0,0,1) mono pou to sigkekrimeno mporei na theorithei oti kanei xirotero fit afou exei perisotera statistika simantika reciduals

ts.plot(x)
acf2(x,50)
sarima(x,1,0,0)
sarima(x,0,0,1)
sarima(x,2,1,2)
  1. ARIMA(2,1,2) (MEAN ABSOLUTE ERROR), mse, mape To sigkekrimeno montelo paratirite oti kanei kalitero fit apo ta proigoumena 2 pou dokimastikan dioti den exei statistika simantika reciduals kathos episis exei kai arketa statistika simantika p-values.

Elenxos MAE, msem mape

for1 <- sarima.for(x[1:length(x-20)],20,1,0,0)
for2 <- sarima.for(x[1:length(x-20)],20,0,0,1)
for3 <- sarima.for(x[1:length(x-20)],20,2,1,2)
print("Model 1 evaluation")
acc1 <- accuracy(for1$pred,x[length(x-20):length(x)])
acc1
print("Model 2 evaluation")
acc2 <- accuracy(for2$pred,x[length(x-20):length(x)])
acc2
print("Model 3 evaluation")
acc3 <- accuracy(for3$pred,x[length(x-20):length(x)])
acc3
# compare RMSE
if ( acc1[2] <= acc2[2] & acc1[2] <= acc3[2] ) {
print("Best Model Is: Model 1")
} else if ( acc2[2] <= acc1[2] & acc2[2] <= acc3[2] ) {
print("Best Model Is: Model 2")
} else {
print("Best Model Is: Model 3")
}
